my-claw/sdp/prd-cypherclaw-sampler.md:110:| CCS-022 | Wire `SampleSelector` into `cast_planner.select_cast_ids` so when the cast includes `sw_sampler`, a sample is pre-selected for the piece and attached to the cast metadata. | MUST | T1 | - `select_cast_ids` (or a sibling `assemble_cast`) returns cast entries with optional `sample_record: SampleRecord` field for sampler voices<br/>- selection happens once per piece commission and passes mode + arc_phase + mood + target_character (drawn from `instrument_patches.select_instrument_patch`)<br/>- tests verify sampler voices in cast carry a sample_record and that the record matches selector contracts |
